  Format & Tips
                                                                                                                                                          
  - Format: JPEG (for photos), WebP preferred (better compression, same quality)                                                                          
  - Quality: Export at 80–85% quality
  - Color space: sRGB                                                                                                                                     
  - Naming: keep it simple, e.g. bridal-lehenga-01.jpg                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                          
  Place images in /public/portfolio/ and reference them as /portfolio/bridal-lehenga-01.jpg in the portfolioItems array.                                  
                                                                                                                                                          
